>Un Aperçu autour de SayMore</titleContent
></titleContentChoices
></secTitle
><p
contentType="en"
>SayMore has only four menu items and three tabs. The menu <object
type="tmenu"
>Session</object
> is greyed out until you clique on the <object
type="tmenu"
>Sessions</object
> tab. This is the same for menu <object
type="tmenu"
>Person</object
> and tab <object
type="tmenu"
>People</object
>.</p
><p
contentType="fr"
>SayMore ne contient que quatre menus et trois onglets. Les menus <object
type="tmenu"
>Session</object
> et <object
type="tmenu"
>Personne</object
> ont la couleur grise quand l'onglet <object
type="tmenu"
>Project</object
> est activé.</p
><figure
contentType="en"
id="fTabs"
><chart
><img
src="images/en/MenusAndTabs.png"
></img
></chart
><caption
>Menu and Tab items</caption
></figure
><figure
contentType="fr"
id="fOnglets"
><chart
><img
src="images/fr/MenusetOnglet_fr.png"
></img
></chart
><caption
>Les menus et les onglets</caption
></figure
><p
contentType="en"
>The next sections will go over what you will find in the Tab layouts.<br
></br
></p
><p
contentType="fr"
>Les prochaines sections vous aideront à trouver les mises en page</p
><section1
id="sProjectTab"
><secTitle
