>Onglet Projet</titleContent
></titleContentChoices
></secTitle
><p
contentType="en"
>The project tab is where you are able to specify and keep track of what the project is about.</p
><p
contentType="fr"
>Cet onglet projet nous permet spécifier et de conserver la description du projet</p
><figure
contentType="en"
id="f-NeedsALabel-.xlingpaper.1..styledPaper.1..lingPaper.1..part.1..chapter.2..section1.1..figure.1."
><chart
><img
