><img
src="images/fr/segment%20automatique.png"
></img
></chart
><caption
>Utiliser le segmenteur automatique</caption
></figure
></li
><li
contentType="en"
>Make sure <object
type="tmenu"
>Use Auto Segmenter</object
> is selected and then click <object
type="tmenu"
>GetStarted</object
>. <br
></br
><p
><object
type="tresult"
>A new window will open and you will see a new file created below your audio clip that is .wav.annotations.eaf</object
> <br
></br
></p
><figure
align="left"
contentType="en"
id="f"
